Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「关于香港的新闻 由于情报不…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了… 小要?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恭子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生体不舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我带你去保健室?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年4班的 千鸟要同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到教师办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像是相良同学寄到事务室来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你别太激动听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟同学…你没事么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 比起这个 里面是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…退学书…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他最近确实总是请假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是连商量都没有 就突然寄来退学书…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道该怎么办了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说呢 千鸟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是怎么回事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是又吵架了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天还没不能联系上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得把这个交给校长处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是说是退学了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 那个家伙已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是有人盯上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是不能回来救你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被监视是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想对策才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能把老师和恭子他们牵连进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是一个只会在塔上叹气的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是情报 必须弄清我身边发生的事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是我多心了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「窃听 偷拍 专用人员为你解除不安!」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是一个人么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吃好吃的吧 我来请客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么酒呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道有个气氛不错的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 我现在很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 想和我去旅馆吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 快点进去吧 水树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面雨很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了水树 大叔我会很用功的哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备选那个房间?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,202房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 还有更好的房间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个看起来很狭小的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开玩笑的 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那间好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水树～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡等下再说 也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦 水树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 是女高中生的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 到底谁是被害者呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说…这个应该没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里的话 周围的情况都可以看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人的话…就一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动 我正用武器瞄准你!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起双手 转过来!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来注意到发信器了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是找我有事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就专程过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以才和陌生男人到那种旅馆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是有些轻视你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 你带抢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢拿出来 扔到脚下!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Mithril的人 是不会对你不利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别得意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不能杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还可以封住你那嚣张的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 更糟糕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近几天 除了我以外还有其他人在跟踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你把抢放下 混蛋!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 千鸟要 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打中吗? 会起作用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是圈套吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被发现了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么圈套吗?会被杀掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是向她求饶才好??!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是专家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能赢他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到这种事情时就不应该心软
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把猎物放在眼前玩弄是三流的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是你赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 认为这世界上有两种女性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合雨景的 和 不适合的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你绝对是前者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到现在的你 谁都会这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在讽刺我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最高级的赞美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你是同类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是来救你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然想这么说 但其实也不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐视不理 也可以来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 结果可能也不会有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人不爽的口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话不能直接一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事情说的太清楚 是会有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可能 这才是你的魅力所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是泰莎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来吧 玉兰 应该已经醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sliver 你有在看?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是你应该应对的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于无视组织一事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以替你辩护求情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能说服在香港暴走的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们会服从吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇什么的 是件非常空虚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是老师的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还活着 就会取那女人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就永别了 玉兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的人是你 雷纳德·泰斯特罗莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请下达指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以A-1处理 给我彻底的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-1处理 结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定的威胁已完全沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 待机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划案1211 Alastor(死刑执行者)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是世界最小的AS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想现在的你应该是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AS的自律行动很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力源和控制系统的微型化也花了我不少精力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是我这次真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看了些煞风景的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不..不明白缘故 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用杀了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈求这种结果的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是是她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还没你的「男朋友」杀的人多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他从小就一直在战争中…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身不由己的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也尽是些坏人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也会救助无辜者或比自己弱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 他绝对没有享受这类事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…他…和你是不一样的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不会这样子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是真的相信这种歪理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方的行为本质都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你 只责怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺会帮着他的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜欢他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是 让睡美人清醒之吻 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我讨厌你 恶心死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜欢上你这点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即虚幻又凶猛 看似粗野却又高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人捉摸不定的 似水的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你还没想杀我之前 我先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是 有事找他的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有理由 要听你的话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原谅你对我所做的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把他给放下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开之前我再说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心喜欢上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 以后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你动不了吗? 受伤了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刚才那男的 注射了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我也是有自尊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种失败…这样的失态…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…还不如这样死了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…你不在这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你不在…才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我…不要这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…待在我身边啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我说“没问题”啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚有说过「不如死了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多抵抗几下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也一直会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}きっと君は今日の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}你今天一定也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}真っ直ぐ明日を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}直视着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}風が吹くあの丘に咲いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}仿佛在那微风吹过的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}向日葵のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}绽放的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}どんなに遠く離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}即使相离再遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}この歌声が君に届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}也要把这歌声传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}涙がずっと止まらない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}在这满脸泪痕的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}君の窓を照らす月になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}希望成为照亮你窗前的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}また必ず会えると そう思うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}一定会再相见的 我这么相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何而战…?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萎缩的心和渐失的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对新的任务 我什么都看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「两个香港」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而后 舞台即将转移到混乱的城市
